aott/analysis/dataflow/reaching_definitions.runa
Reaching Definitions Analysis Module for AOTT Optimization

This module provides reaching definitions dataflow analysis for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Definition-use chain construction
- Variable definition tracking
- Basic block analysis and partitioning
- Forward dataflow computation
- Gen-kill set calculation
- Iterative worklist algorithm
- Definition dominance analysis
- Redundant definition detection
- Cross-function definition propagation
- SSA form integration
- Phi node placement optimization
- Definition liveness tracking
- Constant definition identification
- Loop-carried definition analysis
- Interprocedural reaching definitions
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

